        "basicInfo": "A semi-permanent gathering site used by the Clans of the Long Winter during their seasonal migrations, located in a sheltered valley where natural rock formations provide some protection from the endless winds. The camp represents accumulated generations of survival knowledge, its layout optimized for quick assembly and departure. During gathering seasons, multiple clans meet here to trade, arrange marriages, and settle disputes according to ancient custom.",
