        "hiddenInfo": "Currently, a tense gathering dominates the camp: the noble Silverfang and Ironhowl wolfkin families have convened to finalize an arranged marriage alliance. Jarek Ironhowl, the ambitious patriarch, has been quietly threatening Sigrfid Silverfang for monthshis warriors 'accidentally' slaughtered Silverfang hunting parties, his traders undercut their fur prices, and whispered promises of worse have reached Aldric's ears. The marriage of Jarek's eldest son to Sigfrid's daughter Kira would merge the bloodlines and end the conflict, but everyone knows it would place the Silverfangs under Ironhowl dominance within a generation. Kira Silverfang has discovered the truth her father tries to hide: this is not alliance but surrender under threat. She seeks any alternative that might save her family without sacrificing herself to wolves who see her only as a conquest trophy.Players here may here gossip about the marriage, implication of it and what happened behind the scenes.",
