        "baseLocation": "None",
        "hiddenInfo": "Some clans possess knowledge of ancient ruins and forbidden sites they refuse to share. Internal disputes over dwindling hunting grounds have intensified in recent years. Younger members increasingly question traditions that seem incompatible with survival. There are rumors that certain clans have made pacts with inhuman entities of ice and storm. Clan elders fear cultural extinction as much as physical death.",
